text: Monterey County Fairgrounds is the site of the annual Monterey County Fair. == History == It was the location of the Monterey Pop Festival in 1967. == Musical events == The fairgrounds is the site of the Monterey Jazz Festival as well as First City Festival. == External links == *Official website Category:Music venues in California Category:Buildings and structures in Monterey, California Category:Tourist attractions in Monterey, California
title: Monterey County Fairgrounds
